    "However, considering the number of hallucinations and answers with no references, we give clear preference to the fine-tuned models.",
    "It is worth noting that on a small test set, we have achieved a comparable and sometimes even better performance than GPT-4 Turbo with much smaller, open-source and fine-tuned models.",
    "Having an automated evaluation method of referenced QA quality would allow us to make a more comprehensive comparison of our models to models such as GPT-4 Turbo.",
